These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: blue, lilac, orange, red, green, purple
City: new-york, liverpool, colone, boston, prague, edinburgh
1. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
4. the person traveling to prague is between the person who likes purple and the person traveling to new-york##2
5. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to liverpool##2
6. the person traveling to new-york is the person who likes red##1
7. the person who likes green is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
9. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Color           | blue | lilac | purple | green | red    | orange  |
| City   | edinburgh | liverpool   | boston       | prague        | new-york | colone |

