.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, water, cola, mirinda, 7up, iced-tea
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold, daffodil, azalea, daisy, zinnia
1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person who growsazalea is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
8. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Beverage   | water | iced-tea | 7up | mirinda | cola | juice  |
| Flower           | zinnia | daisy  | bellflower | marigold    | azalea  | daffodil |

