.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  social-worker, architect, security-guard, teacher, firefighter, dancer
6 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, go, snooker, backgammon, canasta
1. the social-worker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the teacher is the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the firefighter##1
5. the security-guard is on the far right##1
6. the firefighter is between the teacher and the person playing scrabble##2
7. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
8. the person playing go is on the right of the teacher##1
9. the architect is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Job         | architect | social-worker | dancer      | firefighter | teacher | security-guard      |
| Game   | monopoly    | canasta  | scrabble | snooker   | backgammon       | go |

