.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, ritmeester, game, swisher, siglo, chaman
There are 6 different favourite colors: amber, red, azure, purple, grey, yellow
1. the person who likes azure is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the left of the game-smoker##1
4. the person who likes purple is the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the bongani-smoker is the person who likes amber##1
6. the person who likes red is between the person who likes amber and the chaman-smoker##2
7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
8. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Cigar        | ritmeester    | chaman | game | bongani | siglo | swisher   |
| Color   | purple | grey        | red  | amber     | yellow  | azure |

