6 different pets are kept: snake, cat, rat, lizard, goldfish, fish
1. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the person who growsazalea is between the person who growsiris and the person who growstulip##2
5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
8. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Flower   | lily   | marigold    | balloon-flower | iris | azalea | tulip   |
| Pet         | goldfish | snake | rat | fish | lizard  | cat |

