.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
6 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, chinchilla, cat, bird, pony
There are 6 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea, water, almond-milk, sprite, milk
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking milk is the owner of the rat##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person drinking water is the owner of the pony##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the cat and the person drinking milk##2
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Pet    | guinea-pig | pony | bird  | cat      | chinchilla | rat  |
| Beverage   | tea  | water    | almond-milk | mirinda | sprite | milk |

