.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  software-developer, nurse, coach, analyst, designer, doctor
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: september, august, october, march, december, july
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the software-developer is between the designer and the analyst##2
4. the analyst is the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the doctor is on the left of the analyst##1
6. the designer is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in december##2
7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
8. the nurse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Job       | doctor | analyst | software-developer | designer | coach | nurse |
| Birthday   | october | july    | december  | september    | march    | august    |

