.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
6 different pets are kept: bird, fish, chinchilla, mouse, horse, snake
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: zinnia, begonia, azalea, balloon-flower, orchid, tulip
1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the person who growstulip is between the person who growsorchid and the person who growszinnia##2
4. the owner of the mouse is the person who growsazalea##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the horse##2
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
7. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
8. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Pet           | mouse | snake | horse | chinchilla | fish | bird |
| Flower   | azalea   | balloon-flower   | begonia         | zinnia    | tulip     | orchid     |

