.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
City: venice, new-york, hamburg, miami, liverpool, boston
There 6 different types of food: plum, nectarine, eggplant, papaya, onion, potato
 1. the person traveling to boston is the person eating papaya##1
 2. the person eating plum is between the person traveling to venice and the person eating potato##2
 3. the person eating nectarine is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating papaya is the person traveling to boston##1
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 6. the person eating papaya is the person traveling to boston##1
 7. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
10. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| City   | venice   | liverpool  | new-york | miami | boston | hamburg     |
| Food   | nectarine | plum | potato    | onion | papaya | eggplant |

