4. the polish is the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the polish is between the malaysian and the german##2
6. the person who growstulip is on the right of the polish##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
8. the dutch is between the malaysian and the person who growsiris##2
9. the chinese is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
| Nationality   | french | dutch | malaysian   | polish | german | chinese |
| Flower           | iris  | lily   | sunflower | begonia | tulip       | dahlia |

