6 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, baccarat, davidoff, game, vegafina, bolivar
 1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 2. the person who likes pink is the vegafina-smoker##1
 3. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 4. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is between the baccarat-smoker and the person who likes grey##2
 6. the game-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 7. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 8. the person who likes blood-red is the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the person who likes lavender is between the dannemann-smoker and the person who likes fuchsia##2
10. the person who likes blood-red is the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Color         | light-blue   | pink | grey       | blood-red | lavender    | fuchsia |
| Cigar   | baccarat | vegafina  | davidoff | dannemann      | game | bolivar        |

