 3. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who growsaconite##1
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who growsbegonia##2
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who's sport is cycling##2
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
 8. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Sport           | soccer      | snowboarding | skateboarding | biathlon   | parkour  | cycling |
| Flower   | aconite | zinnia  | iris             | begonia | daffodil | daisy       |

