.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, mirinda, soy-milk, 7up, sprite
6 different games are played: billiard, whist, mah-jongg, snooker, canasta, go
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the person playing go is between the person playing canasta and the person drinking lemonade##2
 3. the person playing canasta is between the person drinking sprite and the person playing billiard##2
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person drinking mirinda##2
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person playing whist##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | water | 7up   | mirinda     | sprite       | lemonade       |
| Game    | whist | snooker   | billiard | canasta | go | mah-jongg |

