.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-15::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: reading, hiking, skydiving, board-games, baking, card-games
House: art-deco, palace, futuristic, modern, tower, townhouse
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the palace house##1
 2. the modern house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 3. the art-deco house is between the tower house and the palace house##2
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is the art-deco house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the tower house##1
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 9. the futuristic house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
10. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |   5    |     6     |
| Hobby   | card-games | baking    | skydiving     | hiking      | board-games    | reading |
| House   | palace | art-deco | tower | futuristic | townhouse | modern  |

