4. the person driving the car is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
8. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |
| Flower   | marigold   | sunflower   | lily        | balloon-flower   | daisy        | iris   |
| Transport      | helicopter | skateboard | car | motorbike | roller | tram |

