6 different games are played: snooker, domino, scrabble, monopoly, canasta, go
1. the person playing domino is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person playing go##1
3. the person playing monopoly is the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is the person playing snooker##1
6. the person playing canasta is between the person playing domino and the owner of the rabbit##2
7. the owner of the fish is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing scrabble##2
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |         2          |   3    |     4      |       5        |     6     |
| Pet   | bird | fish             | snake  | hedgehog        | guinea-pig       | rabbit    |
| Game        | monopoly    | go | scrabble | domino | canasta | snooker |

