.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: mystery, family, action, documentary, superhero, romance
6 different pets are kept: cat, rat, horse, hamster, lizard, ferret
 1. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is the person watching romance movies##1
 5. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the person watching action movies##1
 8. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 9. the owner of the horse is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
10. the person watching superhero movies is the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Movie-Genre         | documentary | mystery | family | romance | superhero | action |
| Pet   | cat | lizard | horse      | hamster     | ferret       | rat |

 